Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:29.85,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}不论行走到何处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:32.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}暗闇　眺めながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:32.67,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}能做的事情也只有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:37.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}なにもできないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:37.33,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}在黑暗中盲目张望
